data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, NOVEMBER 15TH 2:00-4:00 PM!  PRICE DROPPED $10,000.00!  Welcome home to 3534 Sutton Drive!  STONEBRIDGE VILLAS in award winning PENN HARRIS MADISON SCHOOL DISTRICT!  Villa life at its finest with proximity close to NOTRE DAME, schools, shopping, hospitals, and restaurants!  You will fall in love with this open floor plan home office area, bright & light FOUR SEASON ROOM, and family room with gas log fireplace!  A COOK'S DREAM with your large OPEN KITCHEN with breakfast bar and huge pantry!  Every bedroom has it's own bathroom which is perfect for out of town guests! Upper level bedroom with bathroom and walk-in closet is spacious and private with its own separate stairway!  Master en suite with walk in shower and double vanity sink!  Great outdoor space with private patio! NEW FLOORING INSTALLED IN FAMILY ROOM & SUNROOM in August 2020.  Nothing to do, but move in!  The $305 monthly HOA includes roof, outside maintenance, lawn care, landscaping, spring and fall cleanups, snow removal, water, sewer, trash along with all the clubhouse has to offer including swimming pool!
